slike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"家中淺藍老豆話會投張敏峯<br />\n<br />\n佢話：一個就係社區社體 一個就係為反對自動當選而選<br />\n<br />\n無人要求張隆退選，只係請接受初選勿龜縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b25fdb6c09e44b2d567546b5516a84e9760c45","tid":1490726,"uid":309175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:44:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：曉麗居民"},{"pid":"3b4a9b898a1c3c3188964e8c2ceb92dd11b2dfaa","tid":1490726,"uid":73912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b890a39cb0a7983b89eb1f442df308fbf734099","tid":1490726,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"幾時彈個張隆岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcaea28aea6e0611377a8cda62e8adf6359b0703","tid":1490726,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b890a39cb0a7983b89eb1f442df308fbf734099","tid":1490726,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"幾時彈個張隆岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"受譚香文指使空降"},{"pid":"ed87b3461803db65a10cee2d68c40e2659597333","tid":1490726,"uid":78184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78c7a2d13e2434c9e53f1f1cd3e847dcac4057ed","tid":1490726,"uid":115129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時真係3個選 我睇下張隆過唔過1000票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:51:02.000Z"